<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Custom Design Request</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c6ff 0%, #0072ff 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .request-box { background: #e7f3ff; border-left: 4px solid #0072ff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: #0072ff; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>âœ¨ New Custom Design Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
      
      <p>Congratulations! A customer has requested a custom design from you. Here are the details:</p>
      
      <div class="request-box">
        <strong>Customer Request:</strong><br>
        <strong>Product:</strong> {{productTitle}}<br>
        <strong>Timeline:</strong> {{timeline}}<br>
        <strong>Budget:</strong> {{budget}}<br>
        <strong>Special Requirements:</strong> {{requirements}}
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>What to do next:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Review the customer's requirements</li>
        <li>Submit your design proposal within the requested timeline</li>
        <li>Include sketches or CAD files if possible</li>
        <li>Communicate any questions with the customer</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>This is a great opportunity to showcase your creativity and build a relationship with a customer!</p>
      
      <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="cta-button">{{actionLabel}}</a>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666;">
        Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Engel Fine Design. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
